Overview
An advanced calculator implemented in Ada that handles complex arithmetic operations with parentheses and variable support. This robust implementation features proper expression parsing, operator precedence, and variable management.
Features
Full Arithmetic Support: +, -, *, / with correct precedence

Parentheses Handling: Nested parentheses support

Variables: Store and recall named variables

Error Handling: Comprehensive error detection and messages

REPL Interface: Interactive command-line interface




Input Syntax
Expressions:
(3 + 5) * 2
4.2 / (1.5 - 0.3)

Exiting:
exit





HOW TO USE
COPY THE CODE AND PASTE IT INTO https://www.tutorialspoint.com/compile_ada_online.php
EXECUTE IT